---
// Value proposition section
---

<section class="value-proposition">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="section-header">
			<h2>Why Choose Our Cloud Cost Control Approach</h2>
			<p>We bridge the gap between technical expertise and financial clarity, delivering actionable insights that finance teams can trust and act upon.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="value-grid">
			<div class="value-item">
				<div class="value-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M9 11H15M9 15H15M17 21H7C5.89543 21 5 20.1046 5 19V5C5 3.89543 5.89543 3 7 3H12.5858C12.851 3 13.1054 3.10536 13.2929 3.29289L19.7071 9.70711C19.8946 9.89464 20 10.149 20 10.4142V19C20 20.1046 19.1046 21 18 21H17Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Crystal-Clear Baselines</h3>
				<p>Establish precise baselines for your Azure spend, giving finance teams the concrete data they need to justify budgets and forecast future costs with confidence.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="value-item">
				<div class="value-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 2L13.09 8.26L20 9L13.09 9.74L12 16L10.91 9.74L4 9L10.91 8.26L12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M8 21L9.5 16.5L13 17L9.5 17.5L8 21Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M16 21L17.5 16.5L21 17L17.5 17.5L16 21Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Dedicated Budgeting Frameworks</h3>
				<p>Create clear and actionable budgets tailored specifically to cloud expenditures, building trust through structured insights into cost patterns and anomalies.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="value-item">
				<div class="value-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M14 2H6C4.89543 2 4 2.89543 4 4V20C4 21.1046 4.89543 22 6 22H18C19.1046 22 20 21.1046 20 20V8L14 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M14 2V8H20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M16 13H8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M16 17H8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M10 9H9H8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Monthly Reporting Excellence</h3>
				<p>Deliver detailed monthly reports that ensure consistent engagement, early detection of cost variations, and a strategic roadmap for continuous optimization.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="value-item">
				<div class="value-icon">
					<svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M17 21V19C17 17.9391 16.5786 16.9217 15.8284 16.1716C15.0783 15.4214 14.0609 15 13 15H5C3.93913 15 2.92172 15.4214 2.17157 16.1716C1.42143 16.9217 1 17.9391 1 19V21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M23 21V19C23 18.1645 22.7155 17.3541 22.2094 16.7008C21.7033 16.0474 20.9974 15.5872 20.2 15.3916" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
						<path d="M16 3.13C16.8604 3.35031 17.623 3.85071 18.1676 4.55232C18.7122 5.25393 19.0078 6.11683 19.0078 7.005C19.0078 7.89317 18.7122 8.75607 18.1676 9.45768C17.623 10.1593 16.8604 10.6597 16 10.88" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3>Tech-Finance Bridge</h3>
				<p>Combine technical expertise with financial acumen to help organizations reinvest wisely in scalable technology while maintaining strict cost control.</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="scalable-value">
			<h3>Scalable Value That Grows With You</h3>
			<p>As your organization grows, so does the complexity of managing cloud spend. Our strategic framework helps mitigate surprises in expenses while positioning us as your long-term partner in maintaining financial health.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.value-proposition {
		padding: 100px 0;
		background: #f9fafb;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 24px;
	}

	.section-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 80px;
	}

	.section-header h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #1f2937;
		margin: 0 0 16px;
	}

	.section-header p {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		color: #6b7280;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.value-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
		gap: 32px;
		margin-bottom: 80px;
	}

	.value-item {
		background: white;
		padding: 32px 24px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.value-item:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.value-icon {
		color: #667eea;
		margin-bottom: 24px;
	}

	.value-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1f2937;
		margin: 0 0 16px;
	}

	.value-item p {
		color: #6b7280;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.scalable-value {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 48px;
		border-radius: 16px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.scalable-value h3 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 16px;
	}

	.scalable-value p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		opacity: 0.95;
	}
	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.value-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			gap: 24px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.value-proposition {
			padding: 80px 0;
		}

		.section-header {
			margin-bottom: 60px;
		}

		.section-header h2 {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.section-header p {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}

		.value-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 20px;
			margin-bottom: 60px;
		}

		.value-item {
			padding: 28px 20px;
		}

		.scalable-value {
			padding: 40px 24px;
		}

		.scalable-value h3 {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
		}

		.scalable-value p {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
